To include offices and kindergarten, understand the architects
Administrative building avriopoint in Brno is the new location of arch.design.
No one would have expected that is also miniškolku with all what it includes - with colored walls, nápaditým furniture, a bunch of toys and even miniature playground on outdoor terrace.
Since October last year it may visit the children of employees arch.designu.
Projekčně-architektonická company arch.design, from whose studio came a number of major Brno buildings, counted with space for its corporate miniškolku since the first drawings of buildings avriopoint.
Employs nearly 90 people, mostly in the age of babyboomu and wanted her to make the women projektantky and architektky could quickly go back to work.
Together with the possibility of reduced jobs is a kindergarten benefitem, which arch.design offers its staff in the framework of the social programme.
Stavařky and architektky so they can reconcile the difficult job to care for a child.
Miniškolku have made themselves employees arch.designu and with the support of leadership, they managed to obtain a subsidy of the European Union and the Ministry of Labour and Social Affairs.
Corporate miniškolka is financed from the resources of the European Social Fund through operating the Human Resources and employment and the state budget of the Czech Republic.
Thanks to the grant funding, subsidies of 2, 8 million USD. they can purchase facilities and equipment, and after a period of two years to ensure qualified personnel and operations.
The financial subsidies, for 2 years, the company arch.design has a duty after a period of 3 years to run miniškolku at its own expense.
Preparation project lasted one year, and with the application for the subsidy significantly helped the company economy rating.
Care provides qualified personnel, takes care of children celodenně nurse and a teacher mš, to school so they can walk children without age limits, yet most of them is over 3 years old.
Because it is a "miniškolku," may be present at the same time, only 5 children, during the day but will replace them even more.
Operation of the school is flexible according to the needs of parents and children, all employees have the same right to use kindergarten regardless of the hierarchy of position in the company.
Although this is an individual education and Care Program charge in miniškolce is comparable with the Framework Programme early childhood education.
Children play not only here, but is ensured and quality teaching them - from basic cognition and after preparing to school kids, a professor with the English language.
Class is equipped with not only the toys, podnětnými games, but also the computer, which children can use.
The presence of small children directly in the company creates a friendly and positive environment.
Parents can always check her child and fall stress situation of the late vyzvedáváním children of kindergartens distant from the workplace parents.
Parents and take advantage of working hours more productively.
It is not surprising that, here is naturally loyal relationship employee - employer.
Arch.design so put to Czech companies, which offer significant benefit to recruit new staff, are friendly to the family and strengthened personnel marketing through this program.
Fascinated by House of bones and after 100 years. Look at the Interior from gaudího
Roof looks like a back pravěkého lizards, staircase reminiscent of the backbone of dinosaur and balconies are Open of the mouth.
This is the House measures to Casa batlló in Barcelona from the Catalan architect antoni gaudího.
From local house because of its organic shapes commanded the House of the bones.
Organic shapes, colors, unusual use of rock debris kachlů wild and Mosaic, the facade of scales, and the presence of soft lines, all of this is typical for secessionism antoni gaudího.
The front of the house of one's the quarterback fantasy line, gentle color and texture of nature and animals.
In the detailed observations is seen geometričnost rhythm and precisely measured order.
In the night the entire House facade is even more dramatic, is even umocněn Rightwards, so that was the impression the glamour of colors.
Winding and twisting forms with the equally discovered in the interiors.
Wood in the waves of copying the window frames, rail, decorative elements of the door, watches and bar.
House batlló, which stands in the eixample on the busy shopping street passeig de grácia no. 43, a house from 1877 conversion from architect, Emilio Sala cortese.
Reconstruction was conducted two years and was completed in the year 1906. The House
Investor, a wealthy industrialist, Josep batlló, initially insisted on the demolition of old buildings and creating a completely new, but soon adopted gaudího idea for an unusual and cheaper converting.
Apartment house Casa batlló but antoni gaudí did not suggest himself.
Architect, Josep Maria jujol cooperated with him.
On his projektantském base arose just decoration for representative apartment owner of real estate and use of the facade.
On the facade worked and a number of other creators and artists.
The joint work on the proposals of house Casa batlló started a successful cooperation jujola with gaudím.
Jujol was involved in construction of gaudího House Casa nice and park güell, in which there are other gaudího works.
From the local house soon after the commanded by its organic shapes the nickname "house of bones."
Others him due to the specific mechanism of the opening windows started to "zívajícím house."
Says also that on top of the building is vypodobněn sword St George, the patron of Catalonia.
Hidden religious motives include the other sculptural elements of the building.
Gaudí into the house proposed to its time unique central heating system with odvětrávacími vents and typical chimneys.
Bizarre may seem their forty five stupňový tilt.
When drafting the gaudí totally ignored the tie the building codes and never let them down.
At the beginning of the building had gained from the city of building permits, but it referred to information on the planned reconstruction were so vague that two years later in completing was the result of'm horrified and asked to repair city council.
Local councillor mind, for example, that the construction of running pillars and to the public the sidewalk.
To remedy the never took place, on the contrary, just 15 days after the call of urban areas, Josep batlló applied, and successfully won permission to lease the two top floors buildings.
Himself owner moved into the lower levels.
In the gallery in the second floor was social salon and in the third floor bedroom and private parts of the apartment.
Ground floor was been let jewelry shop.
The šestipatrový House cuts staircase, which can rise to the roof terrace.
Major elements of the reconstruction was the abolition of all the right angles and direct lines and their replacement of the curving walls.
Gaudí also worked with the modern concept of linking space.
Social part can be salonních opens the door completely link and greater company can comfortably communicate together, and he wouldn't at the same time her privacy needed for intimnější talks.
House with gaudího conversion, moreover, in addition to new facades of also unconventional roofs and two floors.
Impressive is also gaudího game with light blue and white glazované tiles, one which is internal auditors, and skylights.
Game two color, adds maximum of light in all the floors of the House.
Enough simply bet on the principle that white reflects the light more than dark, which the sun's rays, on the other hand, drains.
House Casa batlló, which was in the year 2005 included in UNESCO World Heritage Fund, each can visit.
In the first floor of the house is most spacious and nejhonosnější apartment made available to the public.
Owners decided, for this step to in the year 2002, on the occasion of the celebration of one hundred of birth famous artist fiftieth anniversary.
For the controls remained, as they found, that it is a very beneficial business and, moreover, surveys of extended on the common and 6 spaces, including the roof terrace.
Admission to the monuments certainly is not insignificant, is 16,50 euros, pensioners and students, groups and tourist průkazek holders have 20% discount.
Sum greatly exceeds the price of vstupného to other gaudího buildings in the city.
If you want a taste of the mood of the house with dračími turrets, you need to quickly make friends with some of the residents of the house and to visit him right at home.
How to choose the mattress requirements and grid: women have other than men
Not so grand bed frame, but the quality lehací area, mattresses and grid, give the basis of really good bed.
But must be harmoniously complement, to suit the specific users.
In selecting decides lots of things, from the weight, height, age, health and gender owner.
Type of Interior is also essential, in which the mattresses and grid are buying.
A typical example?
To be on the weekend cottages, where isn't regularly, are not appropriate latex mattresses, because the more slowly "heated."
Moreover, have significantly higher than standard weight polyurethane mattresses.
Yet is to be regularly call.
Because if they have a lot of the dump pipes in the heart, and is still lies on the Solid board holds moisture: could the rot under them appear.
In selecting Decides also habit.
Who spent long periods of time in the state, where often used a lot of high mattresses změkčující layer, will find it hard to feel good on low and with the hard surface.
"Perhaps all hockey players from, who were returning from the NHL, had me complained that there is any sleep."
"At His battered the shoulders, heels and hips needed změkčující layer lazy foam mattresses."
"Such recommend even for people with diabetes, who have a breakdown of the nervous system, so badly takes over, the information" from the joints and skin, "explains sylva hadamcziková, which is on the upholstered furniture specialized.
Many hokejistům, but also other customers because years ago sent mattresses with lazy foam.
"Now it's okay, appropriate mattress has to be tempur, Italian magniflex, but also the Czech Tropico."
You don't have to be a guy from the NHL to appreciate lazy foam.
The "miracle" works simply.
Optimize your stiffness and according to the absorbovaného heat or to adjust to your warm form.
Nothing pressing you, at night, you won't tip, as after the game.
You just better sleep.
Lazy foam it works as a protection against proleženinami.
In selecting size mattress to their height add length of feet, which is more about 21 to 34 cm.
A man and a woman with a height of about 180 cm and in need of bed 210 to 220 cm.
The minimum for one should be in dvoulůžka 90 cm, together so 180 cm.
In separate beds, such as the singlistů, recommends at least 120 to 140 cm.
For comfort and possible visit.
"Otherwise, it is a rule to the bed simple: while lying on his back, YOU SHOULD HAVE hands comfortably slightly bent in the elbow," says Ing. Helena prokopová čalouníků Guild, cechmistryně sleeping and dekoratérů, which is the issue of a healthy and ergonomie furniture pays for a number of years and he teaches her on professional schools.
In dvoulůžka needs each own grate and mattress, but watch out here in the purchase of mattress, to reconcile height.
Wrap grids in different heights, otherwise will be nothing other than what you have, however, for each of the frame of the bed may fail.
Foam mattress should have at least 14 cm in height, with spring skeleton at least 15 types, of which at least three centimeters count on forming and raising layer.
"in the hands of contact or dosednutí a mattress spring definitely don't feel," Helena prokopová warns.
Each mattress requires a certain type of grid.
Celočalouněná when beds, mattresses and support, as srostlá Siamese twins, do not have what to do in the bedrooms.
Mattresses wrong větrají, cannot wash their skin, which already today is normal.
And because a night normally vypotíme 0.2 to grapevines sweat, it is clear that after five to seven years mattress will start to a very big, and jammed a sieve.
And therefore, experts reject advertising slogans on the life of the mattress to 25 years, or even a lifetime guarantees.
However, everything has its but.
And that is why the Council of practice from vendors: the mattress with a 120 or 140 cm hygiene and work snímatelný film, but add, a rather mattress buffer, which you cannot give in easily take and wash.
Even if today normally produce mattress covers we get zdrhovadly around the perimeter, so after opening two parts, for money and size of washing machines a lot of important!, yet could handling for the larger types, and when one man in the scan to fight easy with heavy weight in the ring.
You are in bed instead he slid a record?
Never!
Maximum on the bed intended for visit in one night.
Record, however, yet, if it is no longer has of the air vents and use the mattress with spring skeleton and height of at least 15 cm with springs in bags, from něm.taschenfederkern and raising layer.
Polyurethane mattresses on this basis does not belong.
On the nepolohovací laminated grids 14 to 18 lamelami latex will be appropriate or sandwich mattresses, to be a combination of latex and coconut, but you always pays the grids with larger numbers of lamel, 28, and more, where vanes are in the field of European double and it is possible to regulate their stiffness.
On positioning laminated grids are not mattress with spring skeleton, because the positioning unresponsive.
In addition to setting tuhosti lamel can afford even the shoulder the cradle.
It is a special fixing the lamel, which allows push, or even dip lamelu, so as to shoulder a the sleeper "stabbed at items of particular interest."
For men, who have "shoulders through the back" certainly an important thing.
Even remember her mattress and producers, who already in "mens" began to use změkčující zone just in the area of arms.
On the women also remember - those they softer surface again in places hip surgery.
For the most demanding customers are intended křidélkové or destičkové grids with the multitorzním pérováním.
Pressure is to more points and reduce tensions.
But watch out, as soon as you use a mattress and the bad pillow, a large and "naducaný," most of the "plus" disappear.
Basic rule is simple: pillow has support head and on its back with arms, so that they can only intervene to release the shoulder muscles.
As an appropriate size recommends 50 x 60 cm, which prefer, for example, in Scandinavia.
In lying on the side of balance would have a pillow, together with the cradle of, or změkčenou zone in the mattress height on the shoulder.
Modern mattress have with the original slamníky plněnými grasses there is something to do.
Their producers, are increasingly using natural materials or at least matter.
BIO trend is just and with the mattress.
Raw materials from oil, of which are producing polyurethane foam, are replaced natural oils, for example, from skočce and soya.
