A originally as material for NASA, because in the startech astronauts were subjected to enormous congestion.
Tempur in warm soften, in the cold, on the contrary, zpevňuje.
Warm the human body is so perfectly, adjust and dismantles optimal its pressure.
It is therefore ideal against a proleženin, but also for the comfort of while sleeping.
