Apparatus on monitoring people want more and more parents, that they prepare their children
Fear for their own child brings more and more people to the idea of patrol over GPS.
System originally made for search for the cars they may follow the movement of people, and this assistance should be in such cases, which is the disappearance of 9-year-old aničky janatkové.
Device is about the size of a box from matches so far, but may be just a big watch soon.
A number of people said the case of missing aničky and began to better protect the quest for resources, as their children.
Even at the cost of their privacy.
"We have to say that it is not about spying, but on the other means to reduce the probability, that it would be a tragedy," says Peter bits of wood from the company, Macro Weil, which is one of the suppliers surveillance equipment to the Czech market.
"I admit that in a case can be the abuse of such equipment, like to be in the bag when someone who knows about it, but even with such a case we had."
"Most of it really customers are buying for security reasons," he added bits of wood.
According to him, always child should know for what purpose "box" used and how to use in case of an emergency.
Child Psychologist Dana bočková draws attention to the fact that if the child doesn't want to wear anything like it, just get rid of it.
"And very small children show great creativity in it, as some things on purpose to lose if they don't want to be under control."
"The great expectations of earlier on parents' cell phones, which are, however, put off as well as the surveillance equipment," says bočková.
According to her, it is also questionable whether would help in case of attack really such a device.
"If it comes to the kidnapping, it shall be the perpetrator virtually always, to child with him had no electronics, which could reveal his position."
"Now it's phone."
"When they grow a tracking device, will look for and it is, because their sales will certainly supported by a massive advertising."
"In this case, will be criminals always one step ahead of the police," says psychologist.
Acknowledges, however, that such a device may help in the case of a sudden attack pedofilem.
According to Robert čecha from company RC monitoring, which offers tracking service for cars, as well as for persons, and in the case when it comes after the assault for the immediate destruction of surveillance equipment, his presence can help.
"The device can be set to regular sending position after a certain period of time."
"the damage if there would be, will be available for at least the last position of the person concerned."
"More expensive equipment have incorporated and náklonometry, so even if one only slipped and he remained motionless, will send machine immediately warning of an indication of position," says of Bohemia.
According to him, a similar service may divert the smart mobile phones with the navigation, where just load and special software.
Problem of the current surveillance units lies in the fact that it is either an apparatus similar přívěskům box from matches or the smaller size of mobile phones.
Always so threatens their loss.
According to the pilina of macro Weil, so therefore now testing equipment looking like normal digital watch.
"It will have the biggest advantage in the fact that any aggressor does not even recognize a tracking device."
"or is known to after some time and it can give police the extra time," he added.
