Collects money not only from legal business but also from the organized criminal groups.
Each layer of bureaucracy - which Prime Minister Vladimir Putin called "The Office" - will take their, when the money going to move up the ladder.
Record, which was sent to Washington under the name of ambasadora John beyrleho, was on Wednesday made public by The Wikileaks on their Web site.
Record is based on sources, whose names were redigována.
Record was written at a time when he was mayor of still Yuri luzhkov, accusing it of a large part of the corruption.
Was revoked in October, President of the dmitry medvedevem, but since then we can monitor only minimal changes in cleaning.
