The report says that the FSB takes money from the biggest firms and the police focuses on the smaller businesses.
One source," said owners of shops in Moscow are aware that it is better to get protection from the FSB or the Ministry of the Interior, rather than from the organized criminal groups, because they do not have only more weapons, resources and forces than criminal groups, but are also protected by law."
"For this reason, there is no protection from criminal gangs and in course."
Record says that while the selection of money is comprehensive, protection of itself, it might have trouble; and, what is true, you can sometimes be arrested.
Those who don't fast enough, with their business under different pretenses closing.
