Zapatero and red German lines
Berlin decided to maintain the euro, but set conditions for the Union.
Tension in the markets of a double the government response.
On one side of the proposed José Luis Zapatero new adaptation measures, from a reduction in taxes for small and medium sized enterprises, over the regulation of private agencies or lifting 426 euro for the unemployed without benefits, to privatize 49% of the aena, Spanish airports and air traffic management - Yes., manager of airports barajas and El prat and 30% of the national lottery.
Of the Elena salgadová with the support of the former Prime Minister Felipe gonzáleze, on the other hand, join the reviews to address Chancellor Angela Merkel because of its responsibility for initiating the current crisis.
How to interpret this emotion?
It has to be said in advance that the opinion of Merkel is not a mistake in its communication policy.
On the contrary, it is another point in a complex process redefinice of the euro.
And here, Germany has radically new vision of what is supposed to be its future, which faces the idea of compliance with the old traditions, which holds a big part of the other members.
In the face of the European opposition in Germany is beginning to speculate about three possible ways out of the crisis.
The first of them is a strong eurozone, of which would be just part of Germany, but also for example, Austria or the Netherlands, while the South States monetary zone would quit.
The other is a return to the mark - although it may seem as scifi now, this version has broad support from the public, close to 50% of the population.
A third option is under German proposals recasting of the euro, with more macroeconomic surveillance, budgetary severity, fines for guilty States, potentially delaying payments for some of them, and with the expansion of the possible costs for a regulation on the private sector.
German position is clear and already defines some time, so there is no room for evasion by now.
First, when in 2009, the International Monetary Fund, and the European Commission to promote deficits, pulled out of a German Government of constitutional reform, to prevent them from the year 2016.
This was the first sign of a conflict between what it considered Germany right, fiscal stringency plans and stability of the public finances, and this what were his European partners, including France.
The other showed the Central European country, when Merkel sorely protahovala decision on the rescue of Greece.
At that time was the subject of sharp criticism, but the truth is that the political consensus and public opinion, which was also published in Germany, have been strongly opposed to the rescue of Greece.
Finally, days, Merkel once again appeared in the last October with a clear point of view, when called for reform of the Convention of the European Union, so that the purposes of salvation of a Member State, and at the same time, to private creditors have a duty to bear part of the cost.
This opinion was interpreted as opposite of Europe, as accelerate the crisis and all the others.
But the proposal, although in a zmírněné form, was approved, and during the next few months, we should follow the reform process of the Union, which should allow these measures from 2013.
Germany took a red line, which will not exceed.
And all that tells us, although it is now to be done measures, which seems to be too disagree, starting from this date will be the end to an old functioning of the euro.
Year 2013, will be the birth of a new currency zone, in which states that violates rules will be hard penalised and may be forced to announce postponement payments, and the private sector will also have to bear part of the cost.
Germany suggests that we need to give us a strict way to increasing the rate of savings and investment, the moderate consumption growth, improve the productivity and competitiveness, and capital reserves.
No choice based on the claims, and building, with huge gaps in the balance of payments, what was in the years of boom growth of Spain, simply not tolerate.
The offer is clear.
And we made a mistake, we have not understood this.
It is not only about the renewal of the public deficit to 3% in 2013.
It, what they want us to do, is much harder.
And the worst thing is that, under these conditions would happen to us, that the zmýlíme themselves.
I hope that these more calm will replace the current turbulence.
And that we will take the opportunity that they give us into the spring 2013.
It seems that this Prime Minister Zapatero also understood and his double statement after meeting with big enterprises from the reforms promised last Saturday and yesterday's announcement of the new measures, it suggests that over criticism of Merkel opened the way to the idea that there is a need to put things in order.
But the Red line, which Germany itself, there is, and it does not appear that would like to move with her.
