Sport and circumvent rules
Tricks that gave Alonso and Ramos in the match with ajaxem show savvy, not the intention to escape punishment.
Supposedly zosnovaná exclusion of two players Real Madrid, xabiho alonsa and collections Ramos of the Champions League in the match against ajaxu from 23 November caused ink, that was dumped into the sea, about whether or not this is unsportsmanlike behavior, and whether at UEFA should not punish both football players.
As is known, a few minutes before the end of the match, which had their team clearly vyhraný appointed players one after the other deliberately losing time at the moment when the was playing a foul, so as to provoke sudího, and he showed them a second yellow card.
In this way, the two players will fulfil the prescribed punishment in the following match against auxerre - with Real Madrid will end in their group at the forefront of - and, deprived of the cards, will be able to continue on to the next phase.
At the end of the day, the trenéru a UEFA disciplinary commission José mourinhovi punishment in two games and errant players got a cash fine.
Provoking the yellow cards in similar circumstances, there is no new practice, but it is more or less common in football.
Is so widespread that is part of the ethos of football, so the rules, which are an unwritten, but are watching.
Part of the discussion in this case was due to the fact that its participant was team Real Madrid, which is in its hymně boasted about its šlechetností and honour, and which has already for similar actions of his players pokutoval, and as it seems, also thanks to the drama of the mourinhem, which added to its long history of model and a provokatéra another episode.
In any case, the debate revolves around whether this kind of negotiations, which is expressly prohibited rules, so is in violation of the principles of sport, whether in these deeds are respecting sporting rules to circumvent the law; it is indeed a Action, whose sense, however, as it seems, trying to get by.
Solve is, what kind of damage such negotiations are sports spirit.
One of the requirements sportsmanship is the physical integrity of the opponents, which was not violated, or to avoid violent game in these cases.
Another one of these requirements charakterizujících clean game is to prevent players due to its offence had an advantage over team opponent - to which also took place here.
So the players in action, Real Madrid is the fact that this did not happen, what normally charakterizujeme as a trick or circumvent the law, there is a secret breach of rules in order to avoid the penalty, but this behavior should be what is most evident in order to receive the punishment.
Got wait and like a punishment.
Another question, however, is what benefit the guilty of its deliberate violation will have.
It should be noted here that opponent is in a disadvantaged position, and that in the current game can't get no benefit, as an obvious effect is that the team itself will have less players.
And it is not useful strategy in the next game, as the club will not be able with these players count.
Advantage clearly lies in the fact that players will start another phase of the Champions League without cards, which could affect their participation in the future the match.
But it is The advantage in the long term and with a degree of uncertainty, therefore, at first glance, this may be team eliminated, and outside this process will have players punishment and move into the second round of cards, in which about one card is enough to exclusion less than in the first round.
So how will the round continue, will not be fully clear, whether it is the advantage.
In short and well, these negotiations do not go against sporting spirit, part of which is to make the strategic decision, to get the maximum benefit in the framework of the rules.
In the case, which we are dealing here with should not players for target to avoid the penalty, which would be a clear case circumvent the rules, but rather had chosen, when to obey him.
Have made a strategic decision, without stay out of punishment or before him out.
Although borders between wit and circumvention of the rules is not entirely clear, I believe that, in this case, it was clearly a savvy.
It seems to me that a polemic is fueled by two reasons: because this was a two samovyloučení and because of the way it has instructions to transfer their provocation from the leadership.
Damage sports principles of these actions is not so ethical as aesthetic.
