Vindictive hackers and přičinliví spy
The case Wikileaks has two meanings.
On the one hand, it is discovered an apparent scandal scandal, which seems to be the only in the face of hypocrisy, which the relations between states, the people and the press.
On the other hand, speaks about the deep changes on the international level, and anticipates the future ruled by the regression.
But let us move in order.
The first aspect WikiLeaks, it is the fact that each document established secret service, for any nation, consists exclusively of press cuts.
"The extraordinary reported the" Americans on the sexual life of Berlusconi is it, what could read for months each in any of the newspapers, all in addition to these two Berlusconi own, and the karikaturní profile kadáfího was for a long time for entertainer artist topic for the sketches.
Rule, according to which the secret documents may consist only of the reports already known, it is essential in the dynamics of the secret services, and not only in this century.
When you go to a shop, which is dedicated to the ezoterické literature, you'll see that each work repeated, on the graalu, the mystery rennes-le-château, templářích or zednářích exactly what it was written in the previous works.
And not just because the author occult texts to looking for new information, doesn't even know where to find reports about nonexistent, but because those who produce the occult believes only what they already know and what confirms what had previously learned.
It is the success of the Dan Brown mechanism.
The same is true for secret documents.
Informant is lazy, and lazy, or limited spirit, chief of the secret services, and if not, it could be, as I know, an editor at the paper Libération, who asks for true only what he admits.
Information with high confidentiality of Berlusconi, which the American Embassy sent a resort, have been the same, which newsweek published a week before.
So, why is it so much fuss around revelations of these documents?
On the one hand, they say that, while what every cultured man already knows, and that the embassy, at least since the end of the Second World War, and since May heads of states making phone calls or leave the plane to dinner together, lost their diplomatic representation office and, with the exception of a few small exercise in the transformovaly in intelligence.
Any observer of movies about the investigation knows very well that only from licoměrnosti it seemingly Ignoring.
However, the fact that it is repeating itself publicly, dishonours duty of hypocrisy and a bad light on the American diplomacy.
For the other classified information, the idea that Any hacker can get the most powerful country in the world is a severe blow to, not an, for the prestige of the State resort.
Scandal the victims, as well as his "executors."
But let's get from here to deep the truth about what happened.
Once, in times of Orwell's, it was possible to hold all the power, as a Big Brother, who controlled every movement of their people.
