Climate: how France hackla its promises of financing
One year after the Copenhagen agreement it is time to try the compliance with promises to quickly odblokovaná financing, point funding with Quick Start, fast start or premature, realized, developed countries.
And the French hacky were discovered
In Copenhagen agreement with the developed countries committed to provide 30 billion dollars in the years 2010-2012.
The European Union has promised 7.2 billion euros for three years and France 1.26 billion euros, it is 420 million per year.
At the start of EU cop16 pulled out big ace, to convince its partners about the viability of its commitment concerning the financing of the fast start: report specifying the action of its Member States, press conference, Grand side event, the distribution of leaflets...
Transparent operations invaluable and recognized for its real value: the advanced countries and civil society would have to do is all developed countries and civil society as well and with the same level of accuracy.
EU announces that in the year 2010 free up 2.2 billion euros, which brings it to the right way to adhere to its promise of 7.2 billion in the year 2012.
But if we look at the detail, we see that things are much more complicated.
These funds are in Copenhagen agreement "of the new and additional," to ensure that the increased burden is implemented without it would be to the detriment of public assistance for development.
Unfortunately, there is no consensus in what means "new and additional."
While the European Commission proposed the harmonisation block, some Member States, among others, and France, process.
Today, everyone selects the reference, which fits him best.
The European Commission, for example, to see the year 2009: international funding for the reference to preserve and she still adding 150 million to him for three years, financing of fast start.
Other countries choose similar references with annual payment terms or with the timing of the level of public assistance for development.
By contrast, France has considered that "all new projects financing" are "new and additional" by 2010.
In other words, there is no reference to the expenditure of the previous period, or to a global level of public assistance for development d 'aide health in the development.
France in particular, the total amount of aid to the developing countries can remain constant, or even to reduce, has to keep its commitment for "new and additional financing..."
Another key element is the distribution of donations and loans.
There still there is no rule and each of you choose its own way of calculation.
Some, such as France, consider that EUR 1 EUR rental equal to 1, a gift.
Obviously it is difficult to sound: trying to is not přirovnatelná.
If the use of loans can be substantiated for Some investments, which are profitable, often for the projects in more efficient technologies, is linked to the reduction of, of a foolish present one euro, which we'll get as the equivalent of one euro, which we give... should not be understood by virtue of its commitments, but as the price of the loans for věřitelskou country, i.e. the equivalent of interest rates.
But France can give only such reasons: "respects" its commitment of 420 million euros, of which makes 91,5% of the loan, 389,8 million euros and 8.5% of gifts - helped millions of euros of EU - see document to think it could verify themselves.
Is the only countries of the Union, which in the scale of using a loan.
Germany from here, killing 46%, while Denmark, the Netherlands and Slovakia, among others, comply with their commitments with 100% of the donations.
In other words, when the vast majority of the European Union will give EUR 1 for in the framework of the satisfaction to its promise, France can only 10 centimes and considers the effort for a comparable.
Beautiful kejklířský piece!
For summary in its financing "fast start" France is with the dual šejdířstvím: on the one hand with the development of shares in time and on the other hand, with the real financial burden.
Although spends only helped million euros, can convince them that directs 420 million euros "new and additional" in the context of its promises.
Manipulation of Minister of Finance, because it seems that, even though it is bercy double, who was such a decision could have a negative impact, at the same time inside the EU, why would the Member States have continued in the donation, when we need only to lend? - and in negotiations, as developing countries are not quite naive...
Chapter early funding is only a small otázečkou, relatively short, in relation to a series of discussions on the climate.
Moreover, but could be a grain of sand in a huge machine, which is the UNFCCC.
Hopefully, that is not the case.
Whatever it is on, it is necessary to draw the lessons from this first year early funding.
First should France to announce the change in its way of leadership of the accounting for the years 2011 and 2012, in the spirit of respect its commitments and decency and justice for the other countries of the European Union.
But above all, France should avoid debate on deposits in the long term financing, other essential chapter in the present time diskutovaná: neunikneme issue "dodatečnosti" or posting on the loans.
France should change its position, to become pokrokářská for these deposits, as is the case for all.
Hope all inserted into the new Minister for the Environment, the kosciusko-morizetové, which will come to cancunu next week.
Surprising announcement on the fast start of France and its vision of a "dodatečnosti" and the use of loans could cause an increase in the level of international confidence, needed to be to proceed further in the discussions.
