The typical food, including an official recommendation - five pieces of fresh fruit and vegetables, three dairy products and 1.5 litres of water a day - as well as sweets, have been analysed research laboratories to chemical substances, pesticides, heavy metals and other polluting factors.
Balance of Payments plate is overwhelming: 81 chemical substances, of which 42 rank among the carcinogenic, possible or likely, and five substances are among the clear carcinogenic substances, as well as 37 substances that could act as a disruptive for glands to internal secretions, PE, according to the study by several institutions, such as the International Center for Cancer Research.
"Even when legal limits for each chemical adopted in almost all cases individually, in our research are not exceeded Well, we can see that reality in consumer exposure kontaminujícím substances, possibly carcinogenic, and/or PE is amazing," features Association.
